&lt;p&gt;We are recruiting for the role of discharge facilitator to ward 51 at Darlington Memorial Hospital.  The role will involve planning the discharge of patients in a safe, effective and timely manner. The role will involve working closely with the multidisciplinary team.&lt;/p&gt;
